values: 发送；邮寄（信件、包裹等）；传递（信息、信号等）；告知；传达；派遣；使前往；安排去；使作出（某种反应）；使进入（某种状态）；使激动；使兴奋；发射（信号、子弹等）；推动；驱使；使上升；使升高
水流的冲力；波涛的推动力；海浪的冲击力；船的纵摇

pos_mean_info_list.mean: [邮] 寄件人；发送人；发报机
发送；[通信] 发射；信件

word_mean_info__list.difference: 指将文件、消息等的内容或类似的东西发至某地或传达给他人。
普通最常用词，含义广。指把人或物由一地送往另一地，而不涉及事物的内容或 送的方式。
指经过其他人或手段把东西转送给某人。
指把信件、包裹等物寄发出去或交到某地，或直接交与某人，着重发送这一行为。
把通过水运、陆运或空运等方式运送东西。现常指商业上的运货，或将物品托运。
指为特殊目的而发送或派遣，强调紧急或快速。

发出；放出；射出；分发；发给

bilingual.target: 他们每天发送十封电子邮件。

bilingual.source: Let's go online and send this message.
bilingual.target: 我们上网发送这条信息吧。

bilingual.source: When I need to send a message I use code.
bilingual.target: 当我需要发送消息时，我使用密码。

bilingual.source: People are now able to send messages with their voices.
bilingual.target: 现在人们可以用声音发送信息。

bilingual.source: Send in articles about their hands-on learning at school.
bilingual.target: 发送关于他们在学校动手学习的文章。

bilingual.source: Send them to me by email and I'll put them on my webpage.
bilingual.target: 通过电子邮件发送给我，我会把它们放在我的网页上。

bilingual.source: Traditionally, people send written invitations for formal events such as weddings.
bilingual.target: 传统上，人们会为婚礼等正式活动发送书面邀请。

bilingual.source: People can send texts and emails, listen to music, take pictures and videos, and find information online.
bilingual.target: 人们可以发送短信和电子邮件，听音乐，拍照和录像，并在网上查找信息。

list.abstract: send（英 [send]，美 [send]），英语单词，作动词为运送；发送；邮寄。作名词为波浪的推力；波浪引起的水位上升。短语搭配有send out（发出）。例句“Send goods to the quake area.（将货物送到地震灾区。）” send相关近义词有beam、release等。
电影《我的女友是机器人》插曲，演唱者：清竜人

yingyinNormal.en: What? It is not my fault. Why for put Send button right next to Send All? This is just bad design.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？这可不是我的错。你为什么要把发送键放在群发送旁边？这可是不良设计。

yingyinNormal.en: System, locate Dr. Ford for me. Send him a message, highest priority.
yingyinNormal.zh: 系统，帮我定位福特博士，向他发送消息，使用最高优先权。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. Are we never allowed to be alone again? I need to feel loved, too. And send.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我们再也不能单独相处了吗？我也要感受到被爱啊，发送。

yingyinNormal.en: Get everybody off their phones. Hey, no phones. Get people off their computers. Don't hit send.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有人挂掉电话，别打电话，所有人停止使用电脑。别点击发送。

yingyinNormal.en: Even if it does work, the Machine will be so highly compressed that it won't be able to process information, or send signals, or communicate in any way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就算能成功，机器也很可能因为被高度压缩而不能再处理信息，或者发送信号，或者进行交流。

yingyinNormal.en: You shall send a message for me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你帮我传一个讯息。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, we will send them a message.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而我们也要让他们明白。

yingyinNormal.en: Send him back. Charge the drivers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 送他回去，驱动通电。

yingyinNormal.en: What is that? I'll send a dig team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是个什么玩意？我派一个挖掘队过去。

yingyinNormal.en: Then why did you send Milkin to China?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你为什么把米尔金送去中国？

yingyinNormal.en: Go home. Merlin, send in Roxy, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 回家吧。梅林，请洛克希进来吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll send you a postcard. Please, don't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会给你寄明信片。还是别了。

yingyinNormal.en: Why don't you find out? Send them the money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么你不去找找看？把钱交给他们。

yingyinNormal.en: In person? What are we, 30? Send her a text.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当面吗？我们30岁了吗？给她发短信啊。

yingyinNormal.en: That was amazing! I can't even send back soup.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这简直是太神奇了，我连汤都不敢退。

yingyinNormal.en: Please do not send. I enjoy my leisure minute.
yingyinNormal.zh: 求别发，我很珍惜我的空闲时间。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes? The First Lady is here, sir. Send her in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么事？第一夫人来了，先生。 请她进来。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh wait. Did you send those contracts to Milan?
yingyinNormal.zh: 等一下，你有没有把合约寄去米兰？

yingyinNormal.en: Then you must be sure to send her our compliments.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你务必转达我们的致意。

yingyinNormal.en: You're not gonna actually send these out, are you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不是真的要贴出这些照片吧？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: to make something go or be taken to a place, especially by post/mail, email, radio, etc.
sense_info_list.zh: 寄送; 发送; 发射

examination_example.sentence: It <highlight>sends</highlight> a mixed message, and your counterpart gets to choose what signals to read.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它发出了一个混杂的信息，你的对手可以选择解读哪一个信号。

examination_example.sentence: Even without knowing what was in the messages, the knowledge of who <highlight>sent</highlight> them and to whom was enormously revealing and still could be.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 即使不知道这些信息里有什么内容，但知道是谁发送的，是给谁的，仍然具有极大的启示意义。

examination_example.sentence: This universal protection <highlight>sends</highlight> the message: "Please don't approach me."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种普遍的保护传达了一个信息:“请不要接近我。”

sense_info_list.en: cause or order someone to go and do something

examination_example.sentence: It took place on many different planes: between the British and the marshals <highlight>sent</highlight> from Paris to try to keep them in check.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它发生在许多不同的飞机上：在英国人和从巴黎派来的试图控制他们的法国元帅们之间。

examination_example.sentence: A judge might be <highlight>send</highlight> someone to prison if he had already sentenced five or six other defendants only to forced community service on that day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 法官可能会把一个人送进监狱，如果他在那天已经判处了其他五、六名被告强制社区服务。

sense_info_list.en: cause to be in a specified state

examination_example.sentence: The sheer volume of available choice is enough to <highlight>send</highlight> shoppers into a state of information overload.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如此多的选择足以让购物者陷入信息过载的状态。

word_usage.usage: send是可以接双宾语的动词，“给某人邮寄、发送某物”可以说send sth. to sb.也可以说send sb. sth.

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 发报机；发送人；寄件人；送话器

examination_example.sentence: If it is, then you can easily <highlight>send</highlight> it back to the manufacturer, and they'll <highlight>send</highlight> you a brand-new one for free surely.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果是的话，你可以很容易地把它退回给制造商，他们肯定会免费送你一个全新的。

examination_example.sentence: For the first time, messages were <highlight>sent</highlight> electronically across great distances.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 信息第一次以电子方式远距离传送。

examination_example.sentence: Morgan notified the Haslam administration of his decision to opt out in a letter <highlight>sent</highlight> last week.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Morgan 在上周的一封信中通知 Haslam 政府，他决定退出。

sense_info_list.en: cause someone or something to do a particular thing, or to cause something to happen

examination_example.sentence: The problem is that the mere presence of jargon <highlight>sends</highlight> a discouraging message to readers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 问题是，仅仅是行话的存在就会给读者传递一种令人沮丧的信息。

examination_example.sentence: If the wooden frame of the towers had caught fire, it could have <highlight>sent</highlight> the bells crashing down, potentially causing the collapse of both towers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果双塔的木质框架着火，可能会导致钟倾倒，潜在地导致双塔倒塌。

sense_info_list.en: cause or order someone to go and do something
set in motion by physical force

word_usage.usage:
send可表示“使…被送到”，但是没有“赠送（give away）”的含义。
Thank you for sending the flowers.
谢谢你送花。（指的是把花从一个地方运送到另一个地方）

examination_example.sentence: We will <highlight>send</highlight> a van to collect those four and replace them with the Milano you purchased.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们将派一辆货车来收集这四个，并用你购买的米兰替换它们。

examination_example.sentence: But anyway, I'll <highlight>send</highlight> him an email to request a meeting, and I'll see what happens from there.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但无论如何，我会给他发邮件要求会面，然后我再看会发生什么。

examination_example.sentence: Why don't you <highlight>send</highlight> an email requesting a meeting with him in private?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你为什么不给他发封邮件，要求私下见他一面呢？

sense_info_list.en: cause or order someone to go and do something

examination_example.sentence: Joe's parents decided to encourage his creativity by <highlight>sending</highlight> their son to an after-school art class.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 乔的父母决定促进他的创造力，送他们的儿子去上课外美术课。

examination_example.sentence: The scientists first <highlight>sent</highlight> some mice in a specially designed cage to the International Space Station.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科学家们首先将一些装在专门设计的笼子里的老鼠送到了国际空间站。

examination_example.sentence: They would be allowed to <highlight>send</highlight> groups of self-driving cars on cross-state road trips, and even set on-demand fleets of self-driving cars, like the one General Motors and Lyft are building.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们将被允许派遣一批自动驾驶车队进行跨州公路旅行，甚至可以按需组建自动驾驶车队，比如通用汽车和 Lyft 正在建立的车队。

sense_info_list.en: cause someone or something to do a particular thing; or to cause something to happen
set in motion by physical force

examination_example.sentence: If the robot is unsure whether an animal is suitable for the microwave, it has the opportunity to stop and <highlight>send</highlight> out beeps.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果机器人不确定这种动物是否适合使用微波炉，它有机会停下来并发出嘟嘟声。

examination_example.sentence: Whenever I heard of businesses using plastic, I'd <highlight>send</highlight> an email.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每当我听说商家使用塑料，我就发一封电子邮件。

examination_example.sentence: I'd then excuse myself to use the toilet, note down what the beggars said, and <highlight>send</highlight> the information to my teammates.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然后我会找个借口去厕所，记下乞丐们说的话，然后把这些信息发给我的队友。

examination_example.sentence: He likes to think of <highlight>sending</highlight> postcards as a family-friendly hobby.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他喜欢把寄明信片看作是一种有利于家庭的爱好。

examination_example.sentence: Jan 24: National medical teams began to be <highlight>sent</highlight> to Hubei and Wuhan.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1月24日：国家医疗队开始被派往湖北和武汉。

examination_example.sentence: I hear they're going to <highlight>send</highlight> you to Germany for the new project.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我听说他们要派你去德国做新项目。

examination_example.sentence: Welty's new friends immediately <highlight>sent</highlight> a waiter to find a cab.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Welty的新朋友们立刻派了一个服务员去找出租车。

examination_example.sentence: The unwilling parent organizes the meal schedule, <highlight>sends</highlight> out emails, and collects money for end-of-season gifts.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不甘心的家长组织好了用餐时间表，发出邮件，还筹钱准备季末礼物。

examination_example.sentence: Two scientists reported that young maple trees getting bitten by insects <highlight>send</highlight> out a particular smell that neighboring plants can get.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 两位科学家报告说，被昆虫叮咬的小枫树会散发出一种特殊的气味，这种气味邻近的植物也会闻到。

由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 发报机；发送人；寄件人；送话器

word_family.mean: v. 运送；发送；邮寄；发消息；使处于某种状态；颠簸；上升

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 发送消息；发短信；发送短信

sense_info_list.en: cause something to go from one place to another, especially by post or email

examination_example.sentence: Some clothes will be given to the poor and the others will be <highlight>sent</highlight> to factories for recycling.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有些衣服将被送给穷人，其他的将被送到工厂回收利用。

examination_example.sentence: The tradition of <highlight>sending</highlight> birthday cards began in France in the early 18th century.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 寄生日卡片的传统始于18世纪初的法国。

examination_example.sentence: His parents always had him doing lots of housework such as carrying out the rubbish and <highlight>sending</highlight> newspapers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他的父母总是让他做许多家务，如倒垃圾和送报纸

sense_info_list.en: cause or order someone to go and do something

examination_example.sentence: In many places, the government has also built new schools and <highlight>sent</highlight> teachers from the cities to help.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在许多地方，政府还建造了新学校，并从城市派遣教师来支助。

examination_example.sentence: When I was 12 years old, my mother <highlight>sent</highlight> me to a Chinese school in California.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我12岁的时候，妈妈送我去了加州的一所中文学校。

examination_example.sentence: Scientists say one day they could <highlight>send</highlight> robots to build houses on the moon.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科学家说，有一天他们可以派机器人去月球建造房屋。

examination_example.sentence: Something bad or unexpected can happen when people <highlight>send</highlight> up a self-controlled flying machine like a drone.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当人们发射像无人机这样的自控飞行器时，可能会发生一些糟糕或意想不到的事情

examination_example.sentence: The Soviet Union (前苏联) <highlight>sent</highlight> the first space station into space in 1971.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 前苏联于1971年将第一个空间站送入太空。

examination_example.sentence: The first spacecraft with a human was <highlight>sent</highlight> up into space in 1961.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 第一艘载人宇宙飞船是在1961年发射升空的。

word_usage.usage:
send 可以跟双宾语, send sb. sth. = send sth. to sb., 表示“把某物寄给某人”。
如：Don’t forget to send me a letter. = Don’t forget to send a letter to me.
